<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yah̊wah yasūʿu rabãnā
 qad̊ kun̊ta min̊ qab̊li ạl̊jibāl̊
 masarãẗa ạlậbi wamin̊
 qab̊li takawũni ạltĩlạl̊

[V2]
 2- fakun̊ta daẘmaⁿạ ladẖãẗaⁿ
 liqal̊bi ạlậbi fī ʿulạh̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ lam̊ yakun̊ gẖam̊ruⁿ walam̊
 takun̊ yanābīʿu ạl̊mīāh̊

[V3]
 3- fī ạl̊bad̊ʾi lamãạ kẖalaqa
 ạlạảr̊ḍa watẖabãta ạlsãmā
 kun̊ta surūrahu walam̊
 tazal̊ ại̹lay̱ ṭūli ạl̊maday̱

[V4]
 4- lakin̊ naray̱ kulã ạl̊ʿajab̊
 ạảnãhu fī banī ạl̊basẖar̊
 ladẖãạtuka ạl̊ʿuẓ̊may̱ ạlãtī
 faẘqa ạl̊ʿuqūli wāl̊fikar̊

[V5]
 5- faʿajabaⁿạ min̊ niʿ̊maẗiⁿ
 faẘqa ạl̊kẖaṭāyā qad̊ samat̊
 wamin̊ masarãẗiⁿ binā
 qab̊la ạl̊jibāli rusimat̊</lyrics>
<title>yhwh yswʿ rbnạ</title>
</song>